Beam-THE SCALABLE CONFIDENTIAL CRYPTOCURRENCY
Beam——高扩展与强匿名的加密资产

What is BEAM?
什么是BEAM？

BEAM is a next generation confidential cryptocurrency based on an elegant and innovative
Mimblewimble protocol. 
BEAM是下一代强匿名的加密资产，其基于严谨而又革新的Mimblewimble协议构建。

Things that make BEAM special include:
BEAM的特点：

· Users have complete control over privacy - a user decides which information will be available and to which parties, 
having complete control over his personal data in accordance to his will and applicable laws.
· 用户对隐私有绝对控制权——用户可以根据自身意愿和相关可用法律来完全控制自己的信息，其可以决定哪些数据可以公开，哪些机构可以使用这些数据。

· Confidentiality without penalty - in BEAM confidential transactions do not cause bloating
of the blockchain, avoiding excessive computational overhead or penalty on performance
or scalability while completely concealing the transaction value.
· 无需额外资源的隐私交易——在BEAM中，隐私交易不会导致区块链过度膨胀（也不再需要类似Zcash一般消耗大量计算力生成零知识证明），避免了过度消耗计算力对
网络延展性和性能的限制，还能隐藏交易中具体的交易数额。
